    "Generally speaking I am sympathetic to this approach, and the alternative I will suggest in Sect.",
    "\"Current approaches: Outcome-based transparency\" is in essence an extension of these two outcome-based approaches.",
    "However, when comparing the approach to the requirements on transparency from Sect.",
    "\"What kind of transparency do we need?\"",
    "there are two important parts that I think are missed by both Mitchell et al. (2019) and Loi et al. (2021)."
